Nathan Huh (born August 11, 2000) is a computer scientist who is currently an undergraduate at the University of Southern California. He specializes in object-oriented programming and functional programming.

Nathan Huh was born in Busan, Republic of Korea and moved to Cheonan, South Korea to go to boarding school. He graduated Bugil Academy Global Leader Program> in 2019 and enrolled to the University of Southern California. He is taking five courses as a freshman majoring in Computer Science.

He has a personal website built by himself with HTML/CSS.
